	me: Dad, I said it countless of times already.
	dad: That stupid game of yours?
	dad: Quit joking around now. I'm being serious.
	me: Why does it even matter where I got it from?
	me: I saved you[pause=0.5].
	dad: Have you been dealing with shady people, Adam?
