	me: Why do you never believe me?!?!!?!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
	me: You are so close to getting the damn point yet completely missing it at the same time!!!!
	me: I am so sick [pause=0.5]of you all asking me for money for our family for the others family for a family of family everyone and their goddamn mama is profiting off of me for years and years.
	dad: ADAM![pause=0.5] Don't you dare talk to your father like that!!!
	dad: Why are you always like this?!?!?
	dad: Do you even care about me and your mother?!?!!
	me: You think
	me: You really think that I don't care about you?
	me: After all that I've done for you?
